title: Holland Bar Stool Co. 810 Contessa Counter Stool, 25" Seat Height, Graph Anchor
features: 25" Seat Height - Ideal for 35-37" Counter Heights
Heavy-duty, Pewter Powder Coated, 16 Gauge Steel Frame with Solid Mig Welded Construction - BIFMA Load Tested to 550 lbs without Failure - Made in USA
Generously Upholstered 2 1/2" Padded Seat with High Density, U.S.A Made Foam

description: Customize your very own counter stool with the help of the Holland Bar Stool Co. This Pewter Contessa swivel counter stool has a contemporary design and provides superb back support for exceptional comfort. The frame is made from commercial quality 16 gauge, 1 1/4 inch tube steel with solid mig welded joints to guarantee strength and durability. The powder coated finish resists chips and scratches and ensures a long-lasting, rich appearance. The wood seats are 1 1/4 inch solid hardwood (oak or maple) and are dished for amazing posterior comfort, making sitting for minutes or hours a pleasure. The cushion seats are of the highest quality as well, utilizing a breathable, commercial grade vinyl or fabric. At the heart of the cushion is 2 1/2 inches of highly-dense, US made foam that provides maximum support and will not breakdown in a couple years. You won't find a higher quality stool on the market. If you are going to finish your bar or dining area - do it right, with a stool from the Holland Bar Stool Co.
